![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/70b809c7-d156-4f67-852e-87b93452852d/20240819_171656.jpg?format=original)

Randy Orton opens RAW and he's interrupted by GUNTHER who's very angry about the RKO from last week

Gunther asks the crowd if they share three brain cells because all they could come up with was USA chants to support Randy.

Orton is trying to give a rebuttal when he's attacked by Ludwig Kaiser, setting up a match for the main event tonight.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/eb71870b-faaa-4b81-906f-398cdf8a9863/20240819_174653.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_SHEAMUS DEF. PETE DUNNE_**
    

Dunne works Sheamus hand for the entire match, even tieing it down to the ropes at one point. Sheamus breaks out and hits Dunne with the Brogue Kick for the win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3c3ddd73-e5b8-4e9b-8f0c-5efc58382456/20240819_174213.jpg?format=original)

Kofi Kingston confronts Xavier Woods over his attitude the least few weeks. Xavier comes clean about feeling like Odyssey Jones is replacing Big E.

Kofi says he has nothing to worry about

👀

